snippet.title: Ryan Reynolds, Catherine O'Hara Tearfully Accept Governor General's Awards
snippet.description:
Ryan Reynolds and Catherine O'Hara were finally honoured with their Governor General's Performing Arts Awards after a nearly two-year delay. ET Canada's Sangita Patel and Morgan Hoffman react to the hilarious tributes they each received.
#RyanReynolds #CatherineOHara #GGAwards
